Package com.example.chicksevent

Class EntrantJoinWaitlistTest

java.lang.Object
com.example.chicksevent.EntrantJoinWaitlistTest
public class EntrantJoinWaitlistTest extends Object
Unit tests for US 01.06.02: As an entrant I want to be able to join the waitlist from the event details. These tests validate that:
  • Entrants can join the waiting list from event details
  • Entrant is created with correct event ID and user ID
  • Join waiting list operation sets correct status (WAITING)
  • Join waiting list with location data works correctly
  • Firebase operations are called correctly
  • Edge cases are handled properly
